    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape. It\u2019s got a lot of life left in it and drives like a dream\u2014perfect for someone who wants a high-quality car without the 'brand new' price tag. It's been well-loved and taken care of, so you can just hop in and go! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person. Can't wait to hear from you!",
      "price": 32000.0,
